-Damn it,Chandler,stop calling. -Joey,it's Ross.
钱德，别再打来了 乔伊，我是罗斯

14
00:00:50,580 --> 00:00:51,700
-Sorry. -It's all right.
对不起 没关系

15
00:00:51,850 --> 00:00:52,940
What's up?
什么事？ 

16
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:59,040
Not much. I got Chandler here and he's really,really sorry
也没什么 钱德在我这边，他非常非常…

18
