Oh,turkey!
火鸡…

20
00:01:48,300 --> 00:01:50,970
Giving thanks!
说谢谢

21
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:54,740
Look,everyone. It's the spirit of Thanksgiving!
看，这就是感恩节的精神

22
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,200
Are things with Joey better?
你跟乔伊好一点了吗？

23
00:01:57,450 --> 00:02:00,180
They couldn't be worse. I spent eight hours calling him...
糟到不能再糟 我昨晚打了8小时电话给他 

25
00:02:00,420 --> 00:02:02,320
...trying to get him to talk to me.
想让他跟我说上一句话

26
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:05,110
Eight hours.
8小时

27
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:09,080
You could probably use a plug-in telephone headset.
你应该用得上耳机吧？

28
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:13,660
Should we all expect Christmas gifts that are stolen from your office?
我们会收到 你从公司偷来的圣诞礼物吗？

29
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:17,360
You shouldn't.
你不会

30
00:02:19,330 --> 00:02:20,530
Speaking of Christmas....
讲到圣诞节

31
00:02:20,770 --> 00:02:24,670
Since Monica and I are starting a new business and have no money...
摩妮卡和我刚开业，没有钱

32
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:29,540
...this year we could do Secret Santa and each only buy one gift.
今年就来抽签互送吧 这样只要买一份礼物 

34
00:02:29,810 --> 00:02:33,010
And there's the added mystery of who gets who.
还可以猜猜看谁抽到谁

35
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:36,280
Who gets whom.
谁抽到“哪个人”

36
00:02:38,490 --> 00:02:40,510
I don't know why I do that.
我是无意识的

37
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:44,990
But it is correct.
但那样才合文法

38
00:02:45,130 --> 00:02:48,190
Hey,what's this? It's all of your names.
这是什么？ 是你们的名字！

39
00:02:48,330 --> 00:02:50,460
Let's pick.
来抽吧

40
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:54,060
Hey,what's going?
你们在…

41
00:02:55,900 --> 00:03:00,030
-No,Joey,stay. -We're picking names for Secret Santa.
乔伊，不要走 我们要抽签送礼

43
00:03:00,210 --> 00:03:02,180
Okay.
好啦

44
00:03:02,610 --> 00:03:05,440
I invented Secret Santa,you know.
这个做法是我发明的

45
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:10,780
What are you laughing at? You're the one who said Die Hard was your idea.
你笑什么？ 你也说“终极警探” 是你的构想

47
00:03:10,950 --> 00:03:13,180
It was.
本来就是

48
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:17,360
Don't make me show you the napkin.
别逼我把纸巾拿出来

49
00:03:23,460 --> 00:03:26,560
I'm going to take a nap. Turkey makes me sleepy.
我要去睡个觉，火鸡让我爱

50
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,630
We haven't eaten yet.
还没吃耶

51
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:33,740
I know,but all that work you're doing to get it ready and....
我知道，但你那堆准备过程…

52
00:03:35,510 --> 00:03:39,310
Did you pick Rachel for your Secret Santa? I'll trade for her.
你们有人抽到瑞秋吗？我要换

53
00:03:39,710 --> 00:03:43,080
I picked her. Thank God,you want her!
我抽到她，幸好你要她

54
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:45,720
Why do you want to get rid of her so badly?
你为什么这么想换掉她？

55
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:47,850
She exchanges every gift she gets.
因为她收到什么都拿去换 

56
00:03:48,090 --> 00:03:50,490
It's impossible to get her something she likes.
要让她满意根本不可能

57
00:03:50,690 --> 00:03:52,220
Come on,let's trade!
来换吧

58
00:03:52,490 --> 00:03:55,190
I got her that backpack and she loved it.
哪有这回事 她很喜欢我送她的背包

59
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:58,260
I remember she cried when that big dog ran off with
有只大狗把它叼走时 她哭得好…

60
00:04:01,440 --> 00:04:03,230
There was no big dog.
没有什么大狗

61
00:04:04,540 --> 00:04:09,270
This sucks! I already got her a briefcase with "R.G." put on it.
真是的，我已经买了个公事包 还拿去烫了RG

62
00:04:09,740 --> 00:04:12,040
Her initials.
她的姓名缩写

63
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:16,410
Okay,I'm really bad at initials.
我很不会认缩写

64
00:04:17,150 --> 00:04:18,950
You got your shopping done early.
你今年礼物买得真早

65
00:04:19,090 --> 00:04:22,720
Yeah,well,my Camel Cash was about to expire.
我的礼券快过期了

66
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:26,180
Maybe you can give it to somebody else. Like Ross Geller!
也许你可以送给别人 像罗斯盖勒（缩写亦为RG）

68
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:29,360
You know what? It's a girlie briefcase.
那是个女用公事包

69
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:33,100
Who cares! He works in a museum.
那又怎样，他在博物馆上班

70
00:04:34,470 --> 00:04:36,630
The big game's about to start!
现在几点？球赛要开始了

71
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:40,000
Ross and Joey aren't here. You can watch the parade if you want.
罗斯乔伊不在，你可以看游行

73
00:04:40,170 --> 00:04:41,900
Thanks.
谢了

74
00:04:42,980 --> 00:04:45,070
What is wrong with this freezer?
这个冷冻库怎么搞的

75
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:49,150
-What happened? -lce just got in my eye!
怎么了？ 我的眼睛被冰扎到

76
00:04:49,780 --> 00:04:52,810
People are trying to sleep in here!
这里有人要睡觉

77
00:04:53,090 --> 00:04:54,950
Monica got ice in her eye and it hurts!
摩妮卡的眼睛被冰扎到很痛

78
00:04:55,220 --> 00:04:58,120
-Open it up. Let me see. -I can't. It really kills.
张开让我看看 不行，真的很痛

79
00:04:58,390 --> 00:05:00,950
Maybe you should put some ice on it.
也许你应该冰敷

80
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:05,490
-lt looks bad. -We should take you to a doctor.
好像很严重 去看医生好了

81
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:07,560
No,my eye doctor is Richard!
不行，我的眼科医生是理查

82
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:10,630
I can't go to him when I don't have a boyfriend.
我没有男朋友不能去见他

83
00:05:11,170 --> 00:05:13,540
He's really picky about his patients.
他对病患还真挑剔

84
00:05:14,210 --> 00:05:16,700
You've got to go. What's his office number?
你非去不可 他的诊所电话几号？

85
00:05:17,180 --> 00:05:19,580
Like I remember his office number!
我哪会记得

86
00:05:19,780 --> 00:05:21,270
Speed dial seven.
速拨键七

87
00:05:23,990 --> 00:05:26,920
I'm calling on behalf of Monica Geller's eye.
喂，我代表摩妮卡盖勒的眼睛

88
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:31,020
Is Richard Burke in today?
理查柏克今天在吗？

89
00:05:31,690 --> 00:05:33,960
He's not in. Will she see the on-call doctor?
他不在，她愿意看候诊医师吗

90
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:37,460
-Yes. -She's very excited about that!
愿意！ 愿意！她非常兴奋

91
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:40,030
Okay,we'll be right in.
好，我们马上过去

92
00:05:40,170 --> 00:05:42,140
Okay,so who's gonna take her in?
谁要带她去？

93
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:45,300
I'll go,you can watch your parade.
我来，你去看游行

94
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:53,680
It's so cool. Till Monica gets back,I'm head chef.
酷毙了 摩妮卡回来之前，我是主厨

95
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,410
And I get to make all the decisions.
我可以做决定

96
00:05:57,390 --> 00:06:00,250
She told you to follow the recipe exactly.
她叫你完全照食谱来

97
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,220
Get out of my kitchen.
滚出我的厨房

98
00:06:03,930 --> 00:06:06,890
I think I'm making some progress with Joey.
好，我跟乔伊有进展了

99
00:06:07,100 --> 00:06:09,660
When I walked in, he went to his bedroom...
我进门时，他走进他的房间 

100
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:12,870
...but he only slammed the door once.
但只摔了一次门

101
00:06:13,030 --> 00:06:15,800
Yeah,he gave me the finger while doing it.
不过摔的时候有比中指

102
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:21,300
I've got to call my mom and ask her a left-handed cooking question.
我得问我妈左手烹饪的问题

103
00:06:24,010 --> 00:06:26,240
I'm gonna be in there.
我要进房里去 

104
00:06:26,550 --> 00:06:28,780
While I'm gone....
我不在的时候…

105
00:06:31,290 --> 00:06:34,020
Chandler,you're in charge.
钱德，你负责

106
00:06:36,460 --> 00:06:40,450
I picked Monica for Secret Santa,but I'm getting her something for Hanukkah.
我抽到摩妮卡 但我已经替她买了光明节礼物 

107
00:06:40,730 --> 00:06:42,390
You want to switch?
你想换吗？

108
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:45,200
I was trying to trade...
其实我想换成...

109
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:46,460
...for you.
...你

110
00:06:48,870 --> 00:06:51,740
Really? That's so nice. What are you getting me?
真的？真好，你要送我什么？

111
00:06:51,940 --> 00:06:56,740
I don't know,R.G. I was thinking something girlie for your office.
不晓得，RG 某种女性化的上班用品吧

112
00:06:57,710 --> 00:07:00,480
Maybe Phoebe will switch with me.
也许菲比会跟我换

113
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:05,050
Then you'll get stuck with Rachel, and she exchanges every gift.
最好不要，那你会抽到瑞秋 她什么礼物都拿去换

114
00:07:05,290 --> 00:07:08,120
No,I got her lots of stuff she never took back.
乱讲 我送她很多东西她都没退

115
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:09,380
Like?
比如？

116
00:07:09,590 --> 00:07:12,120
Like that gold necklace I got her last year.
像我去年送她的金项链

117
00:07:12,330 --> 00:07:13,730
When did she wear it last?
她上次戴是哪时？

118
00:07:14,230 --> 00:07:18,160
She wore it all Christmas day and then....
她圣诞节整天都戴着，然后…

119
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:20,430
Big dog?
大狗？

120
00:07:27,510 --> 00:07:28,570
What are you doing?
你在干什么？

121
00:07:28,780 --> 00:07:31,300
Sending back this stuff Chandler bought.
把钱德因内疚买的东西退回去

122
00:07:32,010 --> 00:07:35,610
-Even the TV? -No,I'll put that in my room.
全部？包括电视？ 不，电视要搬进房里

124
00:07:37,350 --> 00:07:41,450
Listen,Joey. I know what he did was wrong.
乔伊，我知道他做错了

125
00:07:41,690 --> 00:07:43,420
But can't you hear him out?
但你就不能听他解释吗？

126
00:07:44,030 --> 00:07:47,650
If Chandler had kissed Rachel, would you hear him out?
你和瑞秋在一起的时候， 如果钱德吻了瑞秋，你会听他解释么

128
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,120
That's a good point.
说得好

129
00:07:51,170 --> 00:07:53,500
How long you going to punish him?
那你要罚他多久？ 

130
00:07:53,730 --> 00:07:55,290
Five years.
5年

131
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,490
You've sentenced him?
你还判了刑？ 

132
00:07:57,910 --> 00:08:00,740
Don't do the crime if you can't do the time.
不敢当就不要做

133
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,900
The guy's your best friend.
他是你最要好的朋友 

134
00:08:03,180 --> 00:08:05,010
Was my best friend.
曾经是我最好的朋友

135
00:08:05,210 --> 00:08:07,180
I don't know why you're pushing for him.
你干嘛拼命替他说情？

136
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:12,040
With him out of the way as my best friend,there's a spot open.
少了他碍事 我就没有最要好的朋友了

137
00:08:13,420 --> 00:08:15,950
-Who,me? -Yeah.
我吗？ 对

138
00:08:16,990 --> 00:08:20,930
I'm honored. You know what I'm going to do as your best friend?
我真荣幸 你知道我首先要做什么？

139
00:08:21,330 --> 00:08:23,700
I'm going to get you to talk to Chandler.
拉你去跟钱德说话

140
00:08:25,500 --> 00:08:27,020
All right.
好啦

141
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:29,930
But if you weren't my best friend....
若非你是我最好的朋友…

142
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:34,570
Oh,my God. Is it really that bad?
天哪，真的那么严重？

143
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:37,040
I walk in the room, and he won't talk to me.
我进了门，他根本不理我

144
00:08:37,250 --> 00:08:40,210
He just mumbles something in ltalian.
只念了几句意大利文

145
00:08:41,380 --> 00:08:44,110
And I know he only knows the bad words.
我知道他只会脏话

146
00:08:45,950 --> 00:08:49,580
I'm so,so sorry. I feel responsible.
真对不起，都是我不好

147
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,890
It's not your fault.
不是你的错

148
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:59,360
-Gunther,have you seen Chandler? -I thought you were Chandler.
阿甘，你有看见钱德吗？ 我以为你才是钱德

150
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:04,070
But one of you is over there.
你们其中一个在那边

151
00:09:12,450 --> 00:09:14,740
Hey,Joe.
乔伊

152
00:09:15,154 --> 00:09:16,849
（意大利文）

153
00:09:23,460 --> 00:09:26,760
I'll be right with you. Thanks for coming in.
我马上就好 谢谢你

154
00:09:27,830 --> 00:09:31,960
Oh,my God! How cute is the on-call doctor?
天哪，这个候诊医生真帅

155
00:09:32,470 --> 00:09:36,330
So cute that I'm thinking about jamming this pen in my eye.
帅到我想拿笔插我的眼睛

156
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:49,980
-You have the best luck with eye doctors. -I know.
你的眼科医生缘真好 我知道

157
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:53,020
Dr. Burke will see you now.
柏克医生可以见你了

158
00:09:53,220 --> 00:09:56,920
Not Dr. Burke. The on-call doctor will see me now.
不是柏克医生，柏克医生不在 是候诊医生要帮我看

159
00:09:57,330 --> 00:09:58,590
Dr. Richard Burke is out.
理查柏克医生不在 

160
00:09:58,860 --> 00:10:02,090
Dr. Timothy Burke,his son, will see you now.
他儿子提摩西柏克医生帮你看

161
00:10:03,730 --> 00:10:05,430
Ready?
准备好了吗？

162
00:10:12,310 --> 00:10:14,300
Hey,I'm sorry. That
对不起，刚才…

163
00:10:15,780 --> 00:10:18,470
-Where you going? -My folks'.
你要去哪里？ 我爸妈家

164
00:10:20,450 --> 00:10:21,970
When you coming back?
什么时候回来？

165
00:10:22,220 --> 00:10:26,650
I don't know. I might stay there while I look for an apartment.
不知道 可能会住几天顺便找房子

166
00:10:27,660 --> 00:10:28,640
What?
什么？

167
00:10:29,190 --> 00:10:33,520
I thought we could talk about this. Work it out.
原先我以为我们可以谈开来

169
00:10:33,690 --> 00:10:35,720
Seeing you two together,I don't....
但是看到你们在一起…

170
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:39,230
What do you want me to say? Should I stop seeing her?
你要我说什么？ 说我不见她吗？

171
00:10:39,470 --> 00:10:41,960
It's not about her. Okay?
跟她无关，好吗？

172
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:45,670
But seeing you together reminds me of what you did.
但看到你们在一起 就让我想起你做的事

173
00:10:45,970 --> 00:10:50,470
I won't live with someone who doesn't know what it is to be a friend.
我不跟一个不懂朋友道义的人 住在一起

174
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:54,810
I know what it is to be a friend. I screwed up.
我懂朋友道义，只是我搞砸了

176
00:10:55,050 --> 00:10:56,540
Yeah,you did.
对，没错

177
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:59,540
And that's why I'm leaving.
所以我要离开

178
00:11:00,490 --> 00:11:04,980
If you're not going to stay for me, then at least stay for them.
你不为我留下来 至少为它们留下来

179
00:11:06,190 --> 00:11:09,890
They had a very difficult year. What with the robbery and all.
它们这1年很不顺，还被抢

180
00:11:10,230 --> 00:11:13,330
And that chick used to be very cute.
小鸡本来很可爱的

181
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:15,060
When that guy was robbing us...
当那个人抢了我们 

182
00:11:15,270 --> 00:11:18,100
...and I was locked in the entertainment unit for six hours...
我在柜子里关了6小时

183
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,900
...do you know what I was doing?
你知道我在做什么？ 

184
00:11:20,170 --> 00:11:22,670
I was thinking about how I let you down.
我在想我太让你失望了

185
00:11:24,610 --> 00:11:29,170
If I knew what kind of friend you'd be,I wouldn't have worried.
对，早知道你会见色忘友 我根本不会担心

187
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:34,450
Wait one second! There has to be something that I can do.
等一下…一定有什么我能做的

