00:11:34,660 --> 00:11:36,050
If we still had that unit...
如果柜子还在

189
00:11:36,260 --> 00:11:40,990
...I'd get in it for six hours and think about how I let you down.
我会关6小时 检讨我有多让你失望

190
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:46,690
What?

191
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,600
We got a box.
我们有一个箱子

192
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:54,970
I remember the last time I saw you.
我记得上次见到你 

193
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:57,510
It was the morning I left for college.
是去外地念书的早上

194
00:11:58,380 --> 00:12:00,810
You were standing outside the Dairy Queen.
你站在乳品店外面

195
00:12:02,020 --> 00:12:04,710
Just probably waiting for it to open.
八成是在等它开店

196
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:09,180
-You look great now. -You look great too.
你现在好漂亮 你也很帅

197
00:12:09,660 --> 00:12:11,650
You're an excellent patient.
你真是个好病人

198
00:12:12,730 --> 00:12:13,720
How does it look?
情况如何？

199
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:18,060
You have a scratch on your cornea. You have to wear a patch.
你的角膜有刮伤 得戴几天眼罩

200
00:12:18,370 --> 00:12:20,060
Like a pirate?
像海盗那样？

201
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,530
If that helps you.
你懂就好

202
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:29,840
How long have you been working with your dad?
你跟着你爸多久了？

203
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:33,140
Come on,one of us had to mention him.
总得有人提到他

204
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:36,470
I moved back here a couple months ago.
我是2个月前搬回来的

205
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:39,990
Big family dinner tonight?
晚上要家庭聚餐？

206
00:12:41,090 --> 00:12:42,720
No way!
不会吧

207
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:45,550
I was gonna have Thanksgiving at my girlfriend's.
我本来要去女朋友家吃饭

208
00:12:45,830 --> 00:12:47,380
But we broke up.
但我们分手了

209
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:52,590
She wasn't ready for a serious commitment.
她还不想定下来

210
00:12:55,170 --> 00:12:58,140
So you made her walk the plank, aye,matey?
所以你让她跳海吃自己？

211
00:12:59,310 --> 00:13:00,830
You're not wearing the patch yet.
你还没戴眼罩呢

212
00:13:04,310 --> 00:13:05,940
I know.
我知道

213
00:13:11,650 --> 00:13:14,640
-He's coming here for Thanksgiving? -I know. It's sick.
他要来过感恩节？ 对啊，好变态喔

215
00:13:15,020 --> 00:13:17,680
-Why is it sick? -It's Richard's son!
为什么变态？ 因为他是理查的儿子

216
00:13:17,890 --> 00:13:21,790
It's like inviting a Greek tragedy over for dinner.
这跟找希腊悲剧来吃饭一样

217
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:25,490
If it were Greek, I'd be blind in both eyes.
希腊人会把两只眼睛都蒙住

218
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:30,940
I like him because he's handsome and he's nice and smart and handsome.
我喜欢他的英俊、体帖 聪明和…英俊

219
00:13:32,570 --> 00:13:35,040
Phoebe,you understand,don't you?
菲比，你了解吧？

220
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:38,410
I could see where I'd be your best shot,but no.
我知道你为什么指望我 但是不行

221
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:42,140
Sorry,honey. I think it's twisted.
对不起，我觉得很畸形

222
00:13:42,420 --> 00:13:45,150
-What's twisted? -Me going out with Richard's son.
什么事畸形？ 我跟理查的儿子交往

223
00:13:45,558 --> 00:13:46,991
好恶！

224
00:13:48,327 --> 00:13:49,419
恶恶恶

225
00:13:51,090 --> 00:13:53,150
It sounds like a really bad idea to me.
我觉得实在不太好

226
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:59,830
-ls he okay in there? -He's fine!
他这样可以吗？ 他好得很

227
00:14:00,430 --> 00:14:03,230
If things work out between you and Richard's son...
要是你跟理查的儿子有结果 

228
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:05,060
...you can tell your kids...
你就可以告诉孩子

229
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:07,760
...that you slept with their grandfather.
你跟他们的爷爷上过床

230
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:11,010
Judge all you want to.
随你们怎么批评

231
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:13,580
Married a lesbian, left a man at the altar...
娶到女同志，临阵逃婚 

232
00:14:13,850 --> 00:14:15,320
...Ioved a gay ice dancer...
爱上同性恋冰上舞者

233
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:18,580
...threw a girl's wooden leg in the fire,live in a box!
把女生的木腿丢进火里 睡在箱子里

234
00:14:25,560 --> 00:14:28,620
What exactly is the point of the box?
睡箱子的用意到底何在？ 钱德

235
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:33,990
The meaning of the box is threefold.
有三重意义

236
00:14:34,570 --> 00:14:38,630
One,it gives me the time to think about what I did.
第一，让我有时间反省

237
00:14:39,010 --> 00:14:43,770
Two,it proves how much I care about my friendship with Joey.
第二，证明我有多重视 跟乔伊的友谊

238
00:14:44,450 --> 00:14:45,940
And three...
第三…

239
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:49,280
...it hurts.
会痛

240
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:52,880
And if he stays in the box you guys will be friends again?
他关在里面，你们就能和好？

241
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:55,850
Let's just say it's a start.
这是个开始

242
00:14:56,320 --> 00:15:00,490
Remember that necklace I gave you last year?
记得我去年送你的项链吗？ 

244
00:15:00,660 --> 00:15:02,320
Can I see it?
可以给我看吗？

245
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:04,390
Why?
为什么？ 

246
00:15:04,730 --> 00:15:06,930
I just want to check something.
我只是想看一下

247
00:15:07,370 --> 00:15:08,840
Okay.
好

248
00:15:12,140 --> 00:15:13,570
Now we'll see.
等着瞧吧

249
00:15:13,810 --> 00:15:16,300
Air hole! Air hole!
没气了！没气了

250
00:15:18,150 --> 00:15:21,310
Here it is. I love it. I wear it all the time.
在这里，我很喜欢，我常戴

251
00:15:24,690 --> 00:15:27,850
The necklace I got you was gold. This is silver.
我送的是金项链，这是银的

252
00:15:30,090 --> 00:15:32,520
Well,maybe...
也许它…

253
00:15:33,530 --> 00:15:34,930
...it changed.
变色了

254
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:38,590
Oh,my God! You actually exchanged it.
天哪，你真的拿去换

255
00:15:38,830 --> 00:15:42,000
Isn't it better to exchange it for something I enjoy...
换一个我喜欢又常用的东西 

256
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,530
...and can use a lot?
不是比较好？

257
00:15:43,940 --> 00:15:45,500
What did you get?
你换了什么？ 

258
00:15:45,710 --> 00:15:47,330
Credit.
换购金额

259
00:15:49,980 --> 00:15:53,410
I'll get it. I'll get it. I'll get it. I'll get it. I'll get it.
我来开我来开…

260
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:58,380
Hi,Tim.
提姆

261
00:15:58,920 --> 00:16:02,080
Thank you. Come meet my friends.
谢谢，来见我的朋友

262
00:16:03,420 --> 00:16:04,980
Phoebe.
这是菲比 幸会

263
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:06,490
And Joey.
乔伊 你好

264
00:16:06,730 --> 00:16:08,320
My brother,Ross.
我哥哥罗斯 你好

265
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:10,150
And Rachel.
还有瑞秋

266
00:16:13,130 --> 00:16:14,600
That's Chandler.
那是钱德 

267
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,300
How do you do?
你好

268
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:20,500
-What's? -Well,he's....
这是… 他在…

269
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:22,970
He's doing some thinking.
他在反省

270
00:16:28,450 --> 00:16:31,480
-What happened? -You kissed my girlfriend!
怎么了？ 你亲了我的女朋友

271
00:16:36,160 --> 00:16:37,420
I like those sunglasses.
我喜欢那个墨镜

272
00:16:37,990 --> 00:16:43,120
"Like them" like them? Or "I'd like to get store credit" like them?
是喜欢的喜欢 还是可以换成换购金额的喜欢

273
00:16:44,603 --> 00:16:46,195
（意大利文）

274
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:51,930
This turkey is ready.
各位，火鸡上桌了

275
00:16:52,370 --> 00:16:54,100
Where can I wash up?
哪里可以洗手？ 

276
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:56,140
Let me show you.
来…我带你去

277
00:16:56,610 --> 00:16:58,370
The towels are hanging next to the sink.
毛巾挂在洗手台旁边

278
00:16:58,750 --> 00:17:01,610
-And you can use the fancy soap. -Thank you.
你可以用高级香皂 谢谢

279
00:17:02,820 --> 00:17:06,450
Fancy soap? I thought we were saving that for the pope.
高级香皂？ 我以为要留给教宗用

280
00:17:07,820 --> 00:17:09,550
See. He's nice,right?
他人很好吧？

281
00:17:09,790 --> 00:17:12,920
Do you want a relationship where you can actually say:
但你真的想在谈恋爱时说

282
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:15,820
"That's not how your dad used to do it"?
“你爸的做法不同”？

283
00:17:20,470 --> 00:17:23,130
Everything looks great. Where should I sit?
看起来好好吃，我坐哪里？ 

284
00:17:23,340 --> 00:17:24,330
Saved you a seat.
我帮你留了

285
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:27,300
Sick,sick,sick,sick.
变态变态变态变态

286
00:17:29,610 --> 00:17:31,100
I'll get it.
我去开

287
00:17:31,450 --> 00:17:33,110
Got you!
被我骗了

288
00:17:35,620 --> 00:17:38,110
That doesn't sound like thinking to me.
这听起来不像是反省

289
00:17:38,990 --> 00:17:41,920
-Sorry! -You shouldn't be talking at all.
对不起 你不应该说话

290
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:45,290
You've got too much thinking to do to be talking and joking.
你要想的太多了 不该说话开玩笑

291
00:17:45,630 --> 00:17:47,290
Okay,you got it!
好，没问题

292
00:17:47,490 --> 00:17:49,260
Ross,pass me the yams?
罗斯，把蕃薯给我

293
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:54,090
Joey's got the mashed potatoes if you want to exchange them.
好，你想换的话 乔伊那里有马铃薯泥

294
00:17:57,940 --> 00:18:00,170
Will you stop! What's the matter with you?
够了，你是怎么搞的？

295
00:18:00,810 --> 00:18:03,040
We've got company.
有客人喔

296
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:06,280
Nothing's the matter with me.
我没怎么搞的

297
00:18:06,450 --> 00:18:10,440
I'm not completely devoid of sentiment. I have feelings.
我不是麻木不仁的人 我也有感觉

298
00:18:11,250 --> 00:18:13,480
Okay,fine.
好，很好

299
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:23,260
You can't tell,but I'm breaking the tension by mooning you guys.
你们看不到 但我正在露屁股打圆场

300
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:30,800
All right,look!
听着

301
00:18:31,140 --> 00:18:33,970
If this is a big joke to you, forget about it.
如果你把它当成笑话 那就算了

302
00:18:34,210 --> 00:18:36,200
This means something to me.
这对我很重要

303
00:18:36,410 --> 00:18:39,350
If it doesn't mean anything to you, then get out of there.
要是对你不重要，你就死出来 

304
00:18:39,550 --> 00:18:41,780
Otherwise,you're just an idiot in a box.
否则就太白痴了

305
00:18:42,380 --> 00:18:45,580
You're right. I'm sorry. This means a lot to me.
你说得对，对不起 这对我非常重要 

307
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:50,120
I want to be friends again. I swear I won't say another word.
我想跟你和解 我发誓不会再说话了

308
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:53,650
-So you'll take this seriously? -Absolutely!
你会当一回事？ 绝对会

309
00:18:53,990 --> 00:18:56,220
That sounds like another word to me.
你又说话罗

310
00:18:57,230 --> 00:18:59,500
Are you going to take this seriously?
你会当一回事吗？

311
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:04,940
Okay!
很好

312
00:19:07,010 --> 00:19:09,910
Don't say that I have no sentiment.
别说我麻木不仁

313
00:19:10,880 --> 00:19:13,810
This is a movie stub from our first date.
这是第一次约会的电影票根

314
00:19:14,050 --> 00:19:17,980
This eggshell is from the first time you made me breakfast in bed.
这是你第一次 为我做床上早餐的蛋壳

315
00:19:18,590 --> 00:19:22,720
This is from the museum, the first time we...
这是博物馆的，我们第一次…

316
00:19:22,990 --> 00:19:24,420
...were together.
在一起

317
00:19:25,330 --> 00:19:30,230
Maybe I exchange gifts sometimes, but I keep the things that matter.
我有时会换礼物 但重要的东西我会留

318
00:19:31,530 --> 00:19:33,830
I don't know what to say. I'm sorry.
我不知道该说什么，对不起

319
00:19:34,900 --> 00:19:38,900
Though you're not supposed to take these.
但是…这个不能拿

320
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:44,440
It's,like,a million years old.
它有百万年的历史

321
00:19:45,450 --> 00:19:49,780
We actually have people looking for that.
我们还得派专人去挖

322
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:59,020
-Mind if I smoke? -Care if I die?
我可以抽烟吗？ 想害死我吗？

323
00:19:59,160 --> 00:20:02,930
No,I'm just kidding,I'm just kidding. Go ahead,smoke.
开玩笑的，你抽吧

324
00:20:03,060 --> 00:20:04,620
This always happens.
老是会卡住 

325
00:20:05,230 --> 00:20:06,670
Here,let me.
让我来

326
00:20:07,230 --> 00:20:08,720
Thank you.
谢谢

327
00:20:12,270 --> 00:20:14,240
You have very beautiful...
你有很漂亮的...

328
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:16,670
...eye.
..眼睛

329
00:20:18,580 --> 00:20:20,270
My friends think this is weird.
我朋友都觉得这样很怪 

330
00:20:20,950 --> 00:20:23,310
Even the one in the box?
包括箱子里那个？

331
00:20:24,180 --> 00:20:25,340
It's not weird,is it?
这样不会很怪吧？

332
00:20:26,050 --> 00:20:30,050
I thought it would be. I almost canceled,but it really isn't.
我原先也觉得会，还差点取消 但其实不会

333
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:33,960
I know. Me and your dad, that's totally separate.
我知道 我跟你爸完全是两回事

334
00:20:34,230 --> 00:20:36,160
I totally agree.
我完全同意

335
00:20:36,930 --> 00:20:39,460
We're two people who find each other...
我们只是两个… 

336
00:20:39,830 --> 00:20:41,800
...very attractive.
...互相吸引的人

337
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:43,490
Right?
对吧？

338
00:20:54,410 --> 00:20:57,470
-What? -Nothing,nothing.
怎么了？ 没事

339
00:20:57,820 --> 00:21:00,510
No,really. Was that not okay?
那个吻不好吗？ 

340
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:02,020
No,that was good.
不，很好

341
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:04,750
That was a good kiss.
那个吻很好

342
00:21:05,990 --> 00:21:09,160
-lt reminded you of -Don't say it!
天哪！它让你想到… 别说

343
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,990
-lt did,didn't it? -Yes!
但是有，对吧？ 对！

344
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:14,530
I know!
天哪！ 我知道

345
00:21:17,340 --> 00:21:20,970
God,I am sorry. I am so sorry.
对不起，我真的很抱歉

346
00:21:21,110 --> 00:21:26,140
It's okay. It wouldn't be Thanksgiving without a little emotional scarring.
没关系 少了感情疮疤就不叫感恩节

347
00:21:27,010 --> 00:21:29,070
You know what's even worse?
更糟的是...

348
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:30,740
My friends were right.
我朋友说得对

349
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:36,850
You know what's worst for me is you remind me of a younger version of my mom.
最糟的是 我觉得你就像年轻的我妈

350
00:21:59,280 --> 00:22:02,810
-I want you to know how sorry I am -It's okay.
听着，我真的很抱歉… 没关系

351
00:22:03,020 --> 00:22:07,540
-Chandler's the one I'm mad at. -Well,I'm still sorry.
我气的是钱德 我还是很抱歉

353
00:22:08,560 --> 00:22:11,390
-ls he here? -ln the box.
他在吗？ 在箱子里

354
00:22:20,570 --> 00:22:23,060
He can't talk right now.
钱德？ 他现在不能说话

355
00:22:23,940 --> 00:22:25,430
Why not? What's going on?
为什么？怎么了？

356
00:22:25,810 --> 00:22:28,570
He's trying to show Joey how much he means to him.
他想表示他很重视乔伊

357
00:22:29,740 --> 00:22:32,840
-By being in a box? -Joey had reasons.
所以窝在箱子里？ 乔伊有他的理由

358
00:22:34,510 --> 00:22:35,810
They were threefold.
有三重意义

359
00:22:41,190 --> 00:22:45,680
You not being able to talk might make this easier.
你不能说话反而让事情好办

360
00:22:45,930 --> 00:22:47,830
Listen....
听我说…

361
00:22:57,900 --> 00:23:02,840
I don't want to be someone who comes between two best friends.
听我说 我不想介入两个最要好的朋友

362
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:07,840
I can't stand seeing what this is doing to you guys.
我不忍心看着这件事影响你们 

363
00:23:08,280 --> 00:23:11,050
And I don't want to be the cause of that.
我不想成为罪魁祸首

365
00:23:12,250 --> 00:23:14,550
I don't think we can see each other anymore.
所以我们不该再见面了

366
00:23:15,790 --> 00:23:18,120
I'm going to my mom's in Chicago.
我要去芝加哥找我妈 

367
00:23:18,530 --> 00:23:20,960
I'm going to stay there for a while.
我会住一阵子

368
00:23:26,070 --> 00:23:29,760
I think this could have been something really amazing.
这段感情本来会很美好

369
00:23:29,970 --> 00:23:34,100
But,you know,this is probably for the best.
但这么做最好

370
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:36,600
You know?
你懂吗？

371
00:23:41,450 --> 00:23:43,210
I'm going to miss you.
我会想你的

372
00:23:46,320 --> 00:23:48,310
Goodbye,Chandler.
别了，钱德

373
00:23:57,900 --> 00:23:59,960
Open the box!
把箱子打开啦

374
00:24:00,830 --> 00:24:01,820
What?
什么？ 

375
00:24:01,970 --> 00:24:06,460
He can still catch her. Get out of there! Get out of there!
他还追得上她，快出来啦

376
